title: EYL #169 Miss Diddy on Building a Brand Marketing Empire
itunes:title: EYL #169 Miss Diddy on Building a Brand Marketing Empire
description:
For episode 169 of Earn Your Leisure we spoke with a Los Angeles legend, life style specialist, and marketing phenom. Miss Diddy gave the game on brand partnerships, marketing, deal structure and more. 


She talked about her journey from party promotion to marketing guru. #marketing #missdiddy #brandpartnership 


EYL University: https://www.eyluniversity.com


Guest IG: https://instagram.com/missdiddy?utm_medium=copy_link
